      "review_summary": "The branch awaits the existing memory-core session startup dirty-file scan during status-purpose manager creation and adds a regression test for unindexed session transcripts.\n\nPR surface: Source +13, Tests +22. Total +35 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level. Current main constructs plain status managers as transient, skips session startup catch-up, and status() reports dirty from flags rather than comparing usage-counted session files with indexed sessions rows.",
